text: Samsung Galaxy A03s was released in late 2021. It has a display that has a resolution of 1600 x 720 pixels. It has a 13 MP main, 2 MP depth and 2 MP macro cameras. It has an 8-core processor running at 2.3 GHz with 3 GB of RAM and 32 GB of storage. It supports Wi-Fi 5 (802.11ac) and Bluetooth 5.0.
